*[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"The power of Warlock Part 8: How strange my destiny! Part 6: Am I not dead?"
*"Micronauts Part 8: Adventure into fear!"
